# StudyBuddy 📚

AI Study Assistant that turns lecture notes into summaries, flashcards, and quiz questions in seconds.

## 🌐 Live URL
[Click here to use StudyBuddy](https://your-app-url.lovable.app)

## 🎯 What It Does
Students paste their lecture notes and get:
- 📝 100-word summary with 3 key points
- 🃏 5 flashcards for revision
- ❓ 3 multiple-choice quiz questions
- 📋 One-click copy to clipboard

## 🤖 AI Feature (Custom System Prompt)
When the user submits notes, the AI follows these instructions:

> "You are a patient and encouraging study assistant. Your task is to help students understand complex topics simply. When given notes or text:
> 1. Create a 100-word summary that captures the 3 most important points
> 2. Generate 5 flashcards with questions and answers
> 3. Create 3 multiple-choice quiz questions with correct answers marked with *
> 4. End with one motivational tip
> Keep explanations simple — like explaining to a friend."

## 🛠️ Tools Used
- **Lovable AI** (no-code builder)
- **Built-in AI Connector** (OpenAI/GPT)
- **Tailwind CSS** (styling)
- **LocalStorage** (saves history in browser)

