## 🚀 How to Run
1. Clone the repo: `git clone https://github.com/yourusername/studysnap.git`
2. Open `index.html` in browser (or deploy on Vercel)
3. (Optional) Add API key in .env for AI calls

## 📊 Features
- [x] Paste text input
- [x] AI-powered summary generation
- [x] 5 flashcards with Q&A
- [x] 3 quiz questions with answers
- [x] Copy to clipboard
- [x] Local storage for note history
- [x] Responsive mobile design
